word_group.brief_definition: 有资格为；有能力胜任；符合...的条件

bilingual.source: Without eligible teacher, there can be no high-quality education.
bilingual.target: 没有合格的教师，就不可能有高质量的教育。

bilingual.source: The first thing an eligible adult should know is not tointerruptothers.
bilingual.target: 一个合格的成年人应该懂得的第一件事，是不要干扰别人。

bilingual.source: Of course , before the war, Will would certainly not have been an eligible suitor.
bilingual.target: 在战前威尔当然不是个合格的求婚者.

bilingual.source: And that you were coming of you do an eligible young man against Valence , the previous week.
bilingual.target: 和你的到来，你做一个合格的青年男子对价，较前一周。

bilingual.source: Be otherwise qualified and eligible to receive an award under applicable laws and regulations.
bilingual.target: 或者根据适当的法律和法规,给有资质的合格的投标人授予合同.

bilingual.source: International competitive bidding - ICB: Bidding open to all eligible suppliers and contractors.
bilingual.target: 国际竞争性招标（简写为ICB）；指对所有合格的供应商和承包商开放的招标。

bilingual.source: Superannuation is payable at a minimum of 9 per cent of each eligible employee's earnings base.
bilingual.target: 每个合格的员工至少应按照他们基本工资9%的比例获得退休金。

bilingual.source: Let the Ss read after the teacher. Educate the Ss to follow the traffic rules, and to become an eligible student.
bilingual.target: 同时教育学生在现实生活中要遵守交通规则，做一名合格的中学生。

bilingual.source: Adelia: I've already culled the entries for the ones that don't meet the requirements. These are all eligible.
bilingual.target: 阿德利亚：我已经淘汰了达不到要求的作品。这些都是合格的。

bilingual.source: In order to qualify for an ABA transit number, the financial institution must be eligible to hold an account at a Federal Reserve bank.
bilingual.target: 为了有资格的脱落酸过境人数，金融机构必须持有合格的帐户在美国联邦储备银行。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. It's the most eligible man in New York. How's the moving on going?
yingyinNormal.zh: 全纽约最有身价的单身汉来了，新生活进行得如何呢？

yingyinNormal.en: I happen to know a place where there are plenty of eligible women and Leonard could have his pick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我碰巧知道个好地方，有很多符合条件的女士，莱纳德可以任意选。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.zh: 符合条件的; 合格的

examination_example.sentence: Passengers who pass a background check are <highlight>eligible</highlight> to use expedited screening lanes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 通过背景调查的乘客有资格使用快速安检通道。

examination_example.sentence: If the jobless arrive at the jobcentre with a CV, and register for online job search, they will be <highlight>eligible</highlight> for benefit.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果失业者带着简历来到就业中心，并在网上登记求职，他们将有资格获得福利。

由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

sense_info_list.en: having the right to do or obtain something; satisfying the appropriate conditions

examination_example.sentence: If you are a teenager living in certain parts of the province, you could be <highlight>eligible</highlight> (符合条件) for this program.
